Author-side tooling for InfluxDB 3 plugins.

Usage: influxdb3-plugin <COMMAND>

Commands:
  new       Scaffold a new plugin or index from a built-in template
  index     Inspect a local plugin registry index
  validate  Validate a plugin directory
  package   Validate, archive, hash, and emit a derived index entry
  yank      Toggle the `yanked` flag on an existing index entry
  help      Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help     Print help
  -V, --version  Print version
